<div class="container mt-4">
    <h1 class="mb-4">About the Contract Monthly Claim System (CMCS)</h1>

    <p>
        The Contract Monthly Claim System (CMCS) was developed as part of the
        PROG6212 module to demonstrate the use of secure, efficient, and
        user-friendly systems for processing Independent Contractor lecturer claims.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mt-4">System Purpose</h3>
    <p>
        The system streamlines the workflow of claim submissions, verifications, and
        approvals by providing separate dashboards for <strong>Lecturers</strong>,
        <strong>Programme Coordinators</strong>, and <strong>Academic Managers</strong>.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mt-4">Prototype Stage</h3>
    <p>
        Currently, this is a prototype system designed for demonstration purposes only.
        All data used is fictional and intended to simulate real-world scenarios in
        claim management.
    </p>

    <h3 class="mt-4">Future Enhancements</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Secure authentication and role-based access control</li>
        <li>Integration with institutional payroll systems</li>
        <li>Comprehensive reporting and analytics</li>
        <li>Data encryption and retention policies</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mt-4">
        For more details about our data handling practices, please see our
        <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.
    </p>
</div>